<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Yu-Gi-Oh! Club</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .home-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 40px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .club-header {
            width: 70%;
            max-width: 900px;
            background-color: #4a148c;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 3px solid #222;
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .club-content {
            width: 70%;
            max-width: 900px;
            min-height: 350px;
            background-color: white;
            border: 3px solid #222;
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 40px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .character-side {
            width: 140px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .character-side img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid #222;
        }

        .club-description {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 30px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="home-page">
    <div class="club-header">
        Yu-Gi-Oh! Club
    </div>

    <div class="club-content">
        <div class="character-side left">
            <img src="/images/yugi.png" alt="Yugi image">
        </div>

        <div class="club-description">
            <p>
                Welcome to the Yu-Gi-Oh! Club! Join other duelists to talk about cards,
                strategies, favorite characters, and everything from classic monsters
                to the newest decks. Whether you are a beginner or an experienced duelist,
                there is a place for you here.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="character-side right">
            <img src="/images/kaiba.png" alt="Kaiba image">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>